  "keyFeatures": [
    "Complete tick-by-tick backtesting with customizable time intervals",
    "Full order book reconstruction from Level-2 and Level-3 market data",
    "Accurate latency modeling for feed and order processing",
    "Queue position-based order fill simulation",
    "Multi-asset and multi-exchange strategy support",
    "Live trading bot deployment with same algorithm code",
    "Python API with Numba JIT acceleration",
